-wicked\/","url_meta":{"origin":27524,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplications of oppressed answered, even if wicked","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe supplication of the oppressed is answered, even if he is wicked, for his wickedness is only against himself.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 8795 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32236,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/17\/travelers-parents-oppressed\/","url_meta":{"origin":27524,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Travelers, parents, oppressed answered by Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 17, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Uqbah ibn \u2018Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe supplications of three people are answered: the traveler, the parents, and the oppressed.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 17399 Grade: Hasan li ghayrihi (fair due to external evidence) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0642\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064f\u0647\u064e\u0646\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629"